Modifications made in gate (this internal copy):

  - Removed platform support outside macOS and Linux: dropped
    truststore_windows.go, truststore_freebsd.go and truststore_others.go.
  - Removed Java keystore support: dropped truststore_java.go and the WithJava
    option (gate targets browsers/OS trust only).
  - Added WithLogger(*log.Logger) to route debug output to a caller-supplied
    logger. This is a generic seam; the package still imports nothing from gate.
  - Fixed two debug(err.Error()) calls to use a constant format string
    (debug("%s", err.Error())) so `go vet` passes.

The package remains self-contained (standard library + howett.net/plist on
macOS) and does not import any gate code.
